'''升C小調夜曲, Op. posth.'''是[[蕭邦|蕭邦]]的一首[[夜曲|夜曲]]作品，於1830年創作，獻給其姊Ludwika Chopin，並註“To my sister Ludwika as an exercise before beginning the study of my second Concerto”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.chopin.nifc.pl/chopin/composition/detail/id/52 |title=Narodowy Instytut Fryderyka Chopina |accessdate=2014-02-05 |archive-date=2017-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817160608/http://en.chopin.nifc.pl/chopin/composition/detail/id/52 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Chopin: His Life|last=Murdoch|first=William|year=1935}}</ref>（給我姊Ludwika，為開始我第二首協奏曲前的一個練習）。有時它被稱作“Reminiscence”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.chopin.nifc.pl/chopin/manuscripts/detail/id/250 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-05 |archive-date=2016-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210131251/http://en.chopin.nifc.pl/chopin/manuscripts/detail/id/250 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.amazon.ca/Nocturnes-Comp-Fryderyk-Chopin/dp/B000001GPN |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-05 |archive-date=2010-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105142141/http://www.amazon.ca/Nocturnes-Comp-Fryderyk-Chopin/dp/B000001GPN |dead-url=no }}</ref>（回憶）。

